ssh-proxy-tray (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add local proxy mode option (without system proxy)
    - Add 'Use as system proxy' checkbox in settings dialog
    - Add useSystemProxySetting() to control proxy mode
    - In local mode: only start SSH tunnel, don't configure gsettings
    - In system mode: start SSH tunnel + configure gsettings (default)
    - Update tray tooltip to show proxy mode (System/Local)
    - Auto-reconnect when proxy mode changes

